Name: Ruzh Delta Z
About the game: Ruzh Delta Z is a frenzied shoot-em-up which draws inspiration from classics such as Gradius , DoDonPachi , and R-Type . Shoot your way through perilous stages and wreck thousands of rogue vessels in your quest to become the ultimate pilot. Features Intense non-stop shooting action Bullets, bullets, and more bullets Nail-biting classic shmup gameplay Tons of rogue vessels to destroy Immersive chiptune soundtrack
